{"tid":235781,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"block唔block前度好？","createTime":"2017-05-09T09:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T12:48:36.000Z","uid":12252,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cae5341ba0a1efd687117031c446e6ca21174ce","tid":235781,"uid":12252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:03:27.000Z","msg":"同佢分左手半個月<br />\n有時會八掛睇下佢近況<br />\n其實係我同佢講分手<br />\n因為一直係單方面付出，好辛苦<br />\n我有啲唔捨得<br />\n但如果想復合，我覺得會重滔覆切<br />\n我好想將我既感想同佢講<br />\n我好想知佢有冇愛過我，定係玩我等等呢啲答案<br />\n但冇理由分左手先黎問呢啲<br />\n呢掛發夢都見到佢<br />\n我係咪應該block左佢<br />\n等我以後冇方法搵到佢或知道佢既野<br />\n我應該點做"},{"pid":"76e83eb34e2a62633f70ff8bfc61660fad3bce50","tid":235781,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:04:12.000Z","msg":"Block"},{"pid":"2cb39371c0c9eb139df057cf8b8f169196e66d98","tid":235781,"uid":62651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:04:17.000Z","msg":"Block"},{"pid":"3bcfe84169cf823e30f272982c348f40629ef255","tid":235781,"uid":12252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"應該唔係block<br />\n係直接del左佢"},{"pid":"38faebdb6e51cf585d384431208c6c65c15aeb3f","tid":235781,"uid":12252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:06:13.000Z","msg":"好痛苦啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58462b0f97c13294acf4f1a087a759c9d34d3ae","tid":235781,"uid":45958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"扑，有得扑吾扑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc258c52c34247aa6f61c826933fdb4158b1d6c3","tid":235781,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扑，有得扑吾扑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2829599552ed497cfbcc1ffbab3fe89efa3